      <h2>Want  to be added to our mailing list?</h2>
      <p>Want to receive flyers and news about  Bkejwanong Library events? Send an email to <a href="mailto:library@wifn.org">library@wifn.org</a>, and tell us you'd like to be added to our  mailing list.</p>
